<br>
I think it'd be great RP to be a slave in the manner that Wormtongue was a slave to Sauron at the end of the Lord of the Rings...I'm not into the whole sub/dom thing, but if I made a friend that could make it interesting I'd like to play a minion or henchman.  Tossing me in duels against foes 20 levels higher than me.  Sending me into enemy cities to test their guards, to see if it is possible for my lord to enter.  My master sending me tells so that I can relay information to members of enemy races or far lower levels because he can't be bothered to speak with such &quot;lesser beings.&quot;<br>
<br>
I wouldn't want to be bossed around TOO much though...it's one thing to present that to the world, but another thing to order me around constantly.  It could be great fun though. <p>Reoqim
